                    Barclays global expertise  



















With over 300 years of banking experience we continue to enhance our global footprint, allowing you to realise your opportunities, both at a domestic and global level.
We are committed to working alongside you to drive your success and to help you achieve your ambitions, in the right way. Whatever your business needs or industry, our global expertise empower you to achieve your ambitions in a way that positively impacts the economy and communities. Because when ambitions change lives, we all prosper.
Our Global coverage
Barclays is a global financial services provider with a strong presence in Africa, Asia, Europe and North America.  We are best positioned to offer you strategic and financing solutions across the globe.


Africa
We have a diverse footprint serving clients across Africa our corporate and investment banking division provides you with a full spectrum of financial products to prosper.


Asia
Over 35 years of local banking experience.


Europe
Award-winning banking services for multinationals, benefiting from over 300 years of experience in Europe.


North America
We offer a dedicated team with local and industry expertise in your region.


Source: Barclays, August 2012















































