                    Barclays across Africa  



















Global product knowledge, regional expertise and an extensive, well-established local presence in Africa.
We offer you full support when setting up or expanding your African operations and have a unique presence on the continent, dating back over 100 years. Today, we deliver extensive corporate and investment banking services in 14 countries across Africa and the Indian Ocean.
As the winner of major banking awards, we have the capacity to meet your in-country needs and deliver a wealth of local knowledge. In addition, we’re members of Barclays', giving us one of the largest footprints across Africa.










Our African coverage
Our partnerships are helping to make a positive impact on Africa and her people.

