Company Overview of Absa Capital Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Absa Capital Limited, an investment bank, provides merchant banking, corporate banking, and treasury products to the corporate market in South Africa. Its products and services include corporate finance, investment banking, project finance, trade and commodity finance, capital and debt market products, and treasury and corporate banking, including international banking services, custodial services, and securities lending. The company also serves customers in Africa, the United Kingdom, Europe, and Asia. Absa Capital was formerly known as Absa Corporate and Merchant Bank (Absa Corporate Bank). The company is headquartered in Johannesburg, South Africa. Absa Capital Limited operates as a subsi...
Absa Capital Limited, an investment bank, provides merchant banking, corporate banking, and treasury products to the corporate market in South Africa. Its products and services include corporate finance, investment banking, project finance, trade and commodity finance, capital and debt market products, and treasury and corporate banking, including international banking services, custodial services, and securities lending. The company also serves customers in Africa, the United Kingdom, Europe, and Asia. Absa Capital was formerly known as Absa Corporate and Merchant Bank (Absa Corporate Bank). The company is headquartered in Johannesburg, South Africa. Absa Capital Limited operates as a subsidiary of Absa Bank Limited.
